<author>Patea</author>
<title>Ni Lopi Chu !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nilopi hung tung ding ei tai,
 Ka ngak ui Immanuel;
 Gitloh leh thitha niem ni chu,
 Hukdam chate I chamtatna ding niu.

[V2]
 Zie phat tieng chuleh lawpin la sang ka:
 Lalgam guotsa kumsawt mun ding chang tang ka ting
 A nuom na mai zen ding e, lawp a um na ding e!
 Nun tawp lau loin leng tang ka.

[V3]
 2. Bangtik hi ding ei tam Lalpa,
 Zawh na ni ka muh nang uh;
 Leng in Jordan ka hung kaiha,
 Nang di'n van aksi banga ka vak ding?

[V4]
 3. A hi ngut ie, kumsawt Lalpa,
 Na khawpi satthak achun;
 Na thisana Na chawksate,
 'Ka kawmah hung tauin,' Na ti sek kha.

[V5]
 4. Aw, khawpi thak na hawih ngei ie,
 Na sunga zosate leng;
 A zawhnau la thak sak ding chu,
 Khawvel beih taka dingin a kawihtau.</lyrics>
</song>